e-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap223:3.1":{"pli":"Kilesā jhāpitā mayhaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap223:3.2":{"pli":"bhavā sabbe samūhatā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap223:3.3":{"pli":"Tisso vijjā anuppattā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap223:3.4":{"pli":"kataṁ buddhassa sāsanaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap223:4.1":{"pli":"Ito dvesaṭṭhikappamhi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap223:4.2":{"pli":"tayo āsiṁsu khattiyā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap223:4.3":{"pli":"Ekāpassitanāmā te, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap223:4.4":{"pli":"cakkavattī mahabbalā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap223:5.1":{"pli":"Paṭisambhidā catasso, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap223:5.2":{"pli":"vimokkhāpi ca aṭṭhime; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap223:5.3":{"pli":"Chaḷabhiññā sacchikatā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap223:5.4":{"pli":"kataṁ buddhassa sāsanaṁ”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>"},"tha-ap223:6.1":{"pli":"Itthaṁ sudaṁ āyasmā ālambaṇadāyako thero imā gāthāyo abhāsitthāti. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"tha-ap223:7.1":{"pli":"Ālambaṇadāyakattherassāpadānaṁ paṭhamaṁ. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"tha-ap224":{"tha-ap224:0.1":{"pli":"Therāpadāna ","html":"<article id='tha-ap224'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"tha-ap224:0.2":{"pli":"Ālambaṇadāyakavagga ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"tha-ap224:0.3":{"pli":"Ajinadāyakattheraapadāna ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"tha-ap224:1.1":{"pli":"“Ekattiṁse ito kappe, ","html":"<blockquote class='gatha'><p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap224:1.2":{"pli":"gaṇasatthārako ahaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap224:1.3":{"pli":"Addasaṁ virajaṁ buddhaṁ, ","html":"<span class='v