-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap226:2.1":{"pli":"Tena kammavisesena, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap226:2.2":{"pli":"na passiṁ bhayabheravaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap226:2.3":{"pli":"Kuhiñci upapannassa, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap226:2.4":{"pli":"tāso mayhaṁ na vijjati. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap226:3.1":{"pli":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap226:3.2":{"pli":"yaṁ vediṁ kārayiṁ pure; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap226:3.3":{"pli":"Duggatiṁ nābhijānāmi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap226:3.4":{"pli":"vedikāya idaṁ phalaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap226:4.1":{"pli":"Ito chaṭṭhamhi kappamhi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap226:4.2":{"pli":"apassenasanāmako; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap226:4.3":{"pli":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap226:4.4":{"pli":"cakkavattī mahabbalo. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap226:5.1":{"pli":"Paṭisambhidā catasso, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap226:5.2":{"pli":"…pe… ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap226:5.3":{"pli":"kataṁ buddhassa sāsanaṁ”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>"},"tha-ap226:6.1":{"pli":"Itthaṁ sudaṁ āyasmā ārakkhadāyako thero imā gāthāyo abhāsitthāti. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"tha-ap226:7.1":{"pli":"Ārakkhadāyakattherassāpadānaṁ catutthaṁ. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"tha-ap227":{"tha-ap227:0.1":{"pli":"Therāpadāna ","html":"<article id='tha-ap227'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"tha-ap227:0.2":{"pli":"Ālambaṇadāyakavagga ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"tha-ap227:0.3":{"pli":"Abyādhikattheraapadāna ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"tha-ap227:1.1":{"pli":"“Vi